A clearing in the wood, looks like it was once a small holding. There is a carpet of thyme underfoot that releases a sweet tang into the air as you walk across it.

> x thyme

> x thyme

A powerful herb, Mussolini made the trains run on this stuff
> x hovel

> x hovel

An abandoned and collapsed circular hovel. Amongst its shattered remains you spy what looks like a mug and a fishing rod
> x mug

> x mug

An old brown clay mug, chipped on the rim. On the side it reads 'Mug puns are tea-dious'
