You can see a Broken Bridge, the River Void and Your Dog.

You can go north.

You are on the Northbank of the River Void. The river is roaring past with a fierce current.

> x river

> x river

The River Void is fast, deep and wide. The water level is unusually high and it is roaring loudly as it flows past. It looks like the bridge across has collapsed. On the edge of the riverbank there are a thick beds of reeds.
> x reeds

> x reeds

They are long and fibrous water reeds
> take reeds

