> tie rope to logs

> tie rope to logs

You lash the logs together with the rope, you now have what could very generously be described as a raft. Dylan eyes it suspiciously.
> x raft

> x raft

Your 'artisan' raft, made from four body length logs lashed together with rope
> use raft

> use raft

With some trepidation you launch your raft and jump on, Dylan whimpers and jumps on wth you. Using the shovel as a make shift oar you paddle furiously against the current. Utterly exhausted and shivering you arrive at the Southern Bank of the river and jump off, Dylan follows.

