> give wheat to Wendy

> give wheat to Wendy

"I can mill this for you no problem, about time I got to work anyway, hang on."

 The miller walks over to the wall and pulls a hidden lever, after a few seconds the grindstone begins to move, and you can hear the sails  and gears making a pleasing repetitive , "Koor-keeer, chick-a-clunk.." noise as they spin round.

Wendy empties the wheat into the hopper, and in a few seconds has filled a small sack with flour which she hands to you.
> x flour

